{"tid":2423910,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Jim Cramer指Gme曾計劃買入比特幣轉型或助股價再爆升至430美元","createTime":"2021-02-26T07:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T08:03:50.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7250410d78762e83e169d5ddfb7b34e90d323e23","tid":2423910,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T07:58:05.000Z","msg":"......<br />\n<br />\n隨著GameStop股價因財務長貝爾將離職而上漲，《CNBC》財經節目主持人克萊默25日在其推特上建議，GameStop可以發行10億美元的新股融資，並購買10億美元的比特幣，此舉將助GameStop的股價漲至每股430美元。和25日GameStop收每股108.73美元相比，克萊默預估的價格約高出295%。<br />\n<br />\n克萊默繼續在推特上稱，他推測將離職的財務長貝爾，可能拒絕了GameStop維權股東、董事會成員柯恩（Ryan Cohen）投資比特幣的建議，「柯恩要求董事會以每股200美元的價格，出售1000萬股，並購買比特幣，然後宣稱『現在GameStop遊戲、比特幣都賣』，公司名稱可能改成Bitstop、Gamebit，或Gamecoin，我打賭貝爾拒絕了這個建議」。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3450267\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3450267&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd65q%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=2b87d38b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3450267&h=f4f35518\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3450267</a>"},{"pid":"3606bd19cebc511bc241a0c75bc8cc90f55813aa","tid":2423910,"uid":25357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:00:20.000Z","msg":"咁間間都投資啦<br />\n吹下就升<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b49addeb8e1c4fe0d4217a936a338d0819550c","tid":2423910,"uid":104865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:00:53.000Z","msg":"破釜沉J?"},{"pid":"d2d4be3863d19ce2c87e889b71e16c3246bd254d","tid":2423910,"uid":153976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:01:35.000Z","msg":"唔係32857咩"},{"pid":"74eb9a69f8bd21e3a882232df83e4f666a9fb72f","tid":2423910,"uid":101481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:01:51.000Z","msg":"放低一個bitcoin跟